-- comments are cool
--- 
block comments
conventions:

;   line delimiter
=   assignment
==  equality
<   less than
>   greater than
<   less than or equal
>   greater than or equal
!   logical not
||  logical or
&&  logical and

:   keyword prefix

@   native function
        examples:
            @out
            @install
            @check
            @quit

%   user functions

$   user variables
$$  project variables/constants

#   section header

{}  blocks
[]  lists
()  paremeters
""  string
00  numbers
---